    <item>
      <title>IBM 赢得逆转 BMC 16 亿美元挖角奖</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/ibm-gets-1-6-billion-poaching-award-to-bmc-thrown-out-on-appeal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际商业机器公司 (International Business Machines Corp.) 赢得了一项法庭裁决，推翻了该公司被判于 2022 年向 BMC Software Inc. 支付的 16 亿美元赔偿金，因为该公司在为共同客户 AT&amp;T Inc. 提供服务时更换了自己的软件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/ibm-gets-1-6-billion-poaching-award-to-bmc-thrown-out-on-appeal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 21:48:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚马逊 Twitch 开始在短视频领域与 TikTok 展开竞争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/amazon-s-twitch-starts-rival-to-tiktok-in-short-form-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一项威胁美国社交媒体服务 TikTok 未来的法律通过一周后，亚马逊公司的直播网站 Twitch 推出了自己的短视频平台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/amazon-s-twitch-starts-rival-to-tiktok-in-short-form-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 21:38:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>派拉蒙 CEO 离职，亚马逊、AMD 公布财报 |彭博科技</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-30/paramount-ceo-is-out-and-amazon-amd-report-earnings-bloomberg-technology</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社的卡罗琳·海德和埃德·勒德洛探讨了派拉蒙更换首席执行官的问题，因为并购热潮掩盖了好坏参半的结果。另外：亚马逊、AMD 和 Pinterest 均在盘后发布报告，币安前首席执行官因检察官寻求三年监禁而出庭。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-30/paramount-ceo-is-out-and-amazon-amd-report-earnings-bloomberg-technology</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 21:04:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特斯拉解雇了大部分增压器团队，这对其他汽车制造商来说是一个打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/tesla-axes-supercharger-team-in-blow-to-other-automakers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉公司几乎取消了整个超级充电站组织，该组织已经建立了庞大的公共充电站网络，美国几乎所有主要汽车制造商都在利用该网络。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/tesla-axes-supercharger-team-in-blow-to-other-automakers</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 20:46:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>派拉蒙与宪章同意延长续约谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/paramount-charter-agree-to-extend-talks-on-contract-renewal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，哥伦比亚广播公司 (CBS) 和 MTV 的所有者派拉蒙全球公司 (Paramount Global) 同意延长与付费电视提供商 Charter Communications Inc. 的续约谈判，以防止其有线电视服务频道停止服务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/paramount-charter-agree-to-extend-talks-on-contract-renewal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 20:28:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>AI 芯片预测低于预期后 AMD 股价下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/amd-gives-tepid-forecast-amid-weak-demand-for-gaming-chips</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芯片制造商超威半导体公司 (Advanced Micro Devices Inc.) 对人工智能处理器做出了令人失望的预测，随后其股价在盘后交易中下跌了 9.1%，而人工智能处理器是一个利润丰厚的市场，目前由英伟达公司 (Nvidia Corp.) 主导。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/amd-gives-tepid-forecast-amid-weak-demand-for-gaming-chips</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 20:22:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚马逊报告称，人工智能需求不断增长，云业务销量强劲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/amazon-reports-strong-cloud-unit-sales-on-rising-ai-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司的云部门实现了一年来最强劲的销售增长，这表明随着企业恢复在包括人工智能服务在内的技术项目上的支出，该零售商最赚钱的部门正在从低迷中复苏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/amazon-reports-strong-cloud-unit-sales-on-rising-ai-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 20:12:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>超微销售未能满足投资者的高期望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/super-micro-gives-sunny-sales-outlook-fueling-ai-enthusiasm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[超微电脑公司公布的季度销售额比去年同期增长了两倍，但略低于预期，这令投资者感到失望，他们对这家服务器制造商的业务将受益于人工智能相关的需求抱有极高的期望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/super-micro-gives-sunny-sales-outlook-fueling-ai-enthusiasm</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 20:11:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英特尔股价遭遇数十年来最糟糕的一个月</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/intel-shares-put-up-worst-month-in-decades-with-rebound-elusive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英特尔公司股价 4 月份下跌 31%，是 20 多年来最糟糕的月份，这家芯片制造商仍在努力实现扭亏为盈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/intel-shares-put-up-worst-month-in-decades-with-rebound-elusive</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 17:12:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>PayPal 的支付量在“过渡年”伊始有所上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/paypal-forecasts-decline-in-2024-profit-amid-transition-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于全球消费者支出增加，PayPal Holdings Inc. 第一季度的支付量增长了 14%，提振了该公司早盘交易的股价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/paypal-forecasts-decline-in-2024-profit-amid-transition-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 11:33:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
